eeo policy statement page 1 eeo policy statement slac national accelerator laboratory is principally an institution of scientific research we are leaders in exploring frontier questions of science that enable discovery in our chosen fields we conceive develop build and operate pioneering facilities serving an international user community slac national accelerator laboratory is an affirmative action equal opportunity employer and supports diversity in the workplace slac will take affirmative action to ensure that applicants are employed and that employees are treated during employment without regard to their race color religion sex or national origin age disability veteran status marital status or sexual orientation such action shall include but not be limited to the following employment upgrading demotion or transfer recruitment or recruitment advertising layoff or termination rates of pay or other forms of compensation and selection for training including apprenticeship a diverse workforce is an invaluable asset to innovation and research excellence we are committed to creating an environment in which differences are both welcomed and appreciated we are committed to an inclusive environment where 0 we respect and value individual differences 1 we collaborate and seek out diverse opinions and viewpoints 0 we attract and retain a diverse workforce v our leaders advocate diversity 0 we accept open expression of individuality and diversity within the bounds of courtesy respect and sensitivity the diversity eeo office will audit report and evaluate activities which pertain to our eeo and aa objectives employees who need assistance in the clarification or resolution of eeo matters are encouraged to consult with ill persis s drell director january 30 2012
